SentenceMakingQuestion.content:
You're the project coordinator for a new community initiative. Your boss has asked you to explain how you plan to keep in touch with local organizations to ensure everything runs smoothly.



Emma: 'So, how are you planning to handle communication with our partners?'
SentenceMakingQuestion.solution: I will liaise with the local organizations to ensure we are all on the same page regarding our plans.
